1. **`/init-project`** - Initialize project documentation
2. **`/feature <description>`** - Define WHAT to build (feature requirements)
3. **`/plan-task [description]`** - Plan HOW to build (auto-detects last feature)
4. **`/implement-task [NNN]`** - Implement a task (defaults to latest)
5. **`/test-task [NNN]`** - Test implementation
6. **`/complete-task [NNN]`** - Finalize docs and git workflow
7. **`/fix-bug <description>`** - Quick bug fix workflow
8. **`/document-issue`** - Document a known issue
9. **`/status`** - Show project status
10. **`/review-docs`** - Review documentation
11. **`/update-doc`** - Update documentation

